        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong>, <strong>soy sauce </strong>and <strong>fish sauce </strong>with 700ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[1050ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.4L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1692968766224-x200.jpg",
