        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>hake fillet[s]</strong> into large, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped hake</strong> and <strong>chopped coriander stalks </strong>to the <strong>curried laksa</strong> and cook for 4-5 min further or until the fish is cooked through (discard the lime leaf[ves]) – this is your <strong>curried hake laksa</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
