    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain the<strong> soaked noodles</strong>, then serve in a bowl topped with the <strong>curried hake laksa</strong> and <strong>roasted squash</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>reserved coriander leaves</strong> and <strong>remaining chilli flakes </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
